{"tid":1588544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記協：無綫新聞攝記沙田採訪鏡頭遭噴黑","createTime":"2019-09-23T01:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T08:47:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":443,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":128,"replies":[{"pid":"6849cafdb1d65148bf0c044bce36c865a9d12ece","tid":1588544,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:03:01.000Z","msg":"反修訂《逃犯條例》風波未息，昨午（22日）有示威者破壞沙田站設施，包括塗污逾10部售票機及破壞入閘機。香港記者協會發聲明稱，接獲無綫新聞有攝影器材被噴黑漆的報告，據了解，昨日攝影師於沙田站執行正常採訪職務期間，被人故意噴黑漆阻礙拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n記協譴責這些故意阻礙新聞從業員履行工作職務的行為，並要求各方人士立即停止任何針對新聞工作者的阻礙、干擾或暴力行為。「記協深信，每位前線新聞工作者都忠誠地履行其第四權天職，不容侵犯。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190923/s00001/1569196308509/【逃犯條例】記協-無綫新聞攝記沙田採訪鏡頭遭噴黑\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190923%2Fs00001%2F1569196308509%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94-%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%94%9D%E8%A8%98%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E9%8F%A1%E9%A0%AD%E9%81%AD%E5%99%B4%E9%BB%91&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly4E4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=8f4efe54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190923%2Fs00001%2F1569196308509%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94-%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%94%9D%E8%A8%98%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E9%8F%A1%E9%A0%AD%E9%81%AD%E5%99%B4%E9%BB%91&h=e06b723f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190923/s00001/1569196308509/【逃犯條例】記協-無綫新聞攝記沙田採訪鏡頭遭噴黑</a>"},{"pid":"d940519b566da5f8e8a4bd8e3703d7bda9219279","tid":1588544,"uid":274435,"like":317,"dislike":7,"score":310,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:05:33.000Z","msg":"做法唔完美<br />\n但可接受<br />\n要改善"},{"pid":"25fc3112dc0fe16bc82a3a24489a7836dba18381","tid":1588544,"uid":60563,"like":273,"dislike":1,"score":272,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:05:58.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦冇實